- README file for building external AVS application                       -
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage
-----
1. Build the smbus library. Please follow the instruction provided inside smbus/README file
2. To build the reference application, use the following commands:
  # make clean
  # make
3. Executable will be available inside ./bin folder

4. Execution command :
   1. ./bin/avs_external_test (MDIO)
   2. ./bin/avs_external_test 0x35 0x40 (I2C)
